WITH THE ARRAIGNEMENT AND TRIALL OF NINETEENE NOTORIOUS WITCHES, AT
THE ASSIZES AND GENERALL GAOLE DELIUERIE, HOLDEN AT THE CASTLE OF
LANCASTER, VPON MUNDAY, THE SEUENTEENTH OF AUGUST LAST, 1612.
