[} (^THE VOLUNTARY CONFESSION AND 
EXAMINATION OF^) ELIZABETH DEVICE, (^TAKEN AT THE HOUSE OF^)
IAMES WILSEY, (^OF THE FORREST OF PENDLE, IN THE
COUNTIE OF LANCASTER, THE SEUEN AND TWENTIETH DAY OF
