drinke; both of which particularly appeare.$]

[} (^THE EXAMINATION AND EUIDENCE OF^)
IAMES DEVICE, (^SONNE OF THE SAID^) ELIZABETH 
DEVICE, (^LATE WIFE OF^) IOHN DEVICE, (^OF THE FORREST OF 
